                <h2 style="width: 380px">Trapped by your Inventory?</h2>
                BLS Inventory provides a complete, user-friendly, feature rich integrated environment 
                that supports all general parts distribution business and industry specific activities - 
                including inventory control, purchase orders and sales.
                An Inventory Management System designed specifically for the parts distributor.
